  },
  {
    q: "Do you carry WhisperKool parts on the truck?",
    a: "Common service parts yes — ICU control boards for SC Pro, PDT thermostat replacements for legacy XLT chassis, drain pump motors, condenser fan motors, blower bearings, common run capacitors. Both refrigerant types we use most (R-134a and R-410a) are stocked on the van for same-day recharge work. Less common parts — specific compressor models, proprietary OEM sensor harnesses, certain Platinum Split components — order direct from WhisperKool's Pulaski, Tennessee facility with typical 1-3 business day lead time. We tell you the parts situation during diagnostic so you know whether the repair completes same-day or needs a return visit."
  },

    {
      q: "Where can I find the official WhisperKool manual or warranty information?",
      a: `For official WhisperKool documentation, warranty registration, and authorized service locator, visit <a href="https://www.whisperkool.com/support/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank">WhisperKool support</a>. Our technicians work independently of WhisperKool's factory service network - we're often faster and available same-day in Southern California.`
    },
  ];

